articles.author: Susana Guerrero
articles.title: A new wave of Starbucks closures suddenly hits the Bay Area - sfgate.com
articles.description: Starbucks announced that it plans to close hundreds of stores in North America. This week, a popular store in SF's Castro District announced its closure.
